snippet.title: Zelda 64 Early 1997 Recreation Trailer
snippet.description:
this is the project now it will have maps and stuff from 1996 and early 1997 not sw97 and don't worry an only 1996 version of the game is in progress but that will be after

Special Thanks to the Chriscube Zelda 64 team
and Valentino for some of the textures and assets
